      <title>测试实验室称，痤疮膏中发现与癌症有关的化学物质</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-06/chemical-linked-to-cancer-found-in-acne-creams-testing-lab-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家独立检测实验室在周二晚间向美国食品和药物管理局提交的请愿书中表示，Proactiv、Target Corp. 的 Up &amp; Up 和 Clinique 等品牌的痤疮产品的致癌物质苯含量较高。该实验室表示所有产品都应该被召回。彭博社的西蒙·福克斯曼报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-06/chemical-linked-to-cancer-found-in-acne-creams-testing-lab-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:01:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔预计美联储资本计划将发生“广泛”变化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-06/powell-expects-broad-changes-to-fed-capital-plan-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，央行可能会大幅改变其计划，要求大型贷方持有更多资本。鲍威尔在众议院金融服务委员会作证时发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-06/powell-expects-broad-changes-to-fed-capital-plan-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 15:57:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储鲍威尔：今年可能适当降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-06/fed-s-powell-likely-appropriate-to-cut-rates-this-year-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔在众议院金融服务委员会作证时表示：“委员会预计，在对通胀持续向 2% 迈进更有信心之前，降低目标范围是适当的。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-06/fed-s-powell-likely-appropriate-to-cut-rates-this-year-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 15:47:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙政府警告明年将进一步削减开支</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/macron-s-government-warns-of-harsher-spending-cuts-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预算部长托马斯·卡泽纳夫 (Thomas Cazenave) 表示，即使在今年匆忙进行了一轮削减以实现赤字削减目标之后，法国政府在 2025 年可能仍需要大幅增加储蓄。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/macron-s-government-warns-of-harsher-spending-cuts-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 15:33:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔重申美联储需要对通胀更有信心才能降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/powell-reiterates-fed-needs-more-confidence-on-inflation-to-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔向立法者重申，在政策制定者确信他们已经赢得了对抗通胀的战斗之前，美联储并不急于降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/powell-reiterates-fed-needs-more-confidence-on-inflation-to-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔重申降息消息，债券增加近期涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/treasuries-fall-ahead-of-powell-s-remarks-and-us-jobs-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔在国会作证时重申了他 1 月份传达的信息——美国国债市场近期上涨。如果通胀数据继续显示改善，今年可能会降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/treasuries-fall-ahead-of-powell-s-remarks-and-us-jobs-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 09:01:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
