      <title>鲍威尔成为焦点，股市上涨，债券收益率下降：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市上涨，债券收益率下跌，杰罗姆·鲍威尔重申，预计美联储将在 2024 年降息——同时仍表明官员们在经济强劲的情况下并不急于这样做。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 22:46:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
